s be upon him, said, \u201cThere will be rulers appointed over you who delay the prayer from its proper times and invent new heresies.\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cWhat should I do if I see them?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou ask me,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36602,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/06\/rulers-huquq\/","url_meta":{"origin":36611,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rulers: What if they do not give us our rights?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Wa\u2019il al-Hadrami reported: Salamah ibn Yazid asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cO Prophet of Allah, what do you think if rulers are charged over us who demand their rights and prevent us from our rights? What do you command us to do?\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2044,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/05\/follow-sunnah-beware-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36611,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Follow the Prophet, beware of innovation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-\u2018Irbad ibn Sariyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prayed with us one day. Then, he faced us and delivered an eloquent sermon that brought tears to our eyes and hearts were shaken by it. It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, it is as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36609,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/06\/sabr-unless-disobedient\/","url_meta":{"origin":36611,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rulers: Patience with tyranny but no obedience in sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cListen and obey authorities in hardship, in ease, and in what you dislike, even if they give undue preference over you, even if they consume your property and they strike your back, unless they order\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5611,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/27\/fear-allah-pray-obey-leaders\/","url_meta":{"origin":36611,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Fear Allah, pray your prayers, obey your leaders","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said in his farewell sermon, \u201cFear Allah your Lord, pray your five prayers, fast your month of Ramadan, give charity from your wealth, and obey those in authority over you. You will enter the Paradise of your Lord.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u064